milestones.description: New Zealand's 309 is the highest total in ODIs, surpassing England's 266
Glenn Turner and John Parker's 149-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 143 between Alvin Kallicharran and Fredericks
Glenn Turner's 171 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing David Lloyd's 116
Glenn Turner has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (76) in an innings in ODIs, going past Majid Khan's 70
Glenn Turner and John Parker's 149-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Mike Denness and David Lloyd
Glenn Turner has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (76) in an innings in ODIs for NZ, going past Ken Wadsworth's 64
Glenn Turner has become the top scorer for NZ in ODIs with 244 runs, going past Bevan Congdon's 237
Hastings has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for NZ, going past Bevan Congdon
Glenn Turner's 171 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NZ), surpassing Ken Wadsworth's 104
Glenn Turner and John Parker's 149-run partnership is NZ's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 130 between Ken Wadsworth and Bevan Congdon
Glenn Turner and John Morrison's 51-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Glenn Turner and Peter Coman
Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth's 52-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 39 between John Parker and Peter Coman
Glenn Turner and John Parker's 149-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 84 between Bevan Congdon and Hastings
